import React from'react'
import {Link, NavLink} from 'react-router-dom'
import Panel from './Panel'
const Navbar = () => {

    const baseClass = 'tex-blue-500'
    const activeClass = 'text-blue-500 border-l-4 font-bold decoration-solid'
    return <Panel className ="sticky top-0 overflow-y-scroll flex flex-col item-start">
        <NavLink 
        to ="/" 
        className={({isActive}) => 
          // isActive is a prop we get for free from NavLink
          isActive ? activeClass : baseClass
        }
        >
        Button
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink to ="/" className="text-blue-500">
        Accordion
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink to ="/" className="text-blue-500">
        Dropdown
        </NavLink>

    </Panel>
}
export default Navbar
